OL,3,CPlaque to honour 100 years since
OL,4,CHollywood actor Richard Burton's birth
OL,6,FToday, 10 November, marks 100 years
OL,7,Fsince the birth of one of Wales' most
OL,8,Fcelebrated actors, Hollywood legend
OL,9,FRichard Burton.
OL,11,FTo mark his centenary, a series of
OL,12,Fevents have been organised across the
OL,13,Fcountry, including the unveiling of a
OL,14,Fcommemorative plaque at his childhood
OL,15,Fhome in Pontrhydyfen.
OL,17,FBorn in 1925 in Pontrhydyfen, a small
OL,18,Fvillage in the Afan Valley, Neath Port
OL,19,FTalbot, Burton rose from humble
OL,20,Fbeginnings.
