OL,4,CHollywood actor Richard Burton's birth
OL,6,FHe was the 12th of 13 children born to
OL,7,Fcoal miner Richard Jenkins and his
OL,8,Fwife Kate, though tragically two of
OL,9,Fhis siblings did not survive infancy.
OL,11,FWhen Richard was just two years old,
OL,12,Fhis mother died from septicaemia, and
OL,13,Fhe was subsequently raised by his
OL,14,Fsister, her husband, and their two
OL,15,Fyoung daughters.
OL,17,FDespite these challenges, Burton
OL,18,Fdeveloped a passion for literature and
OL,19,Facting, performing in local plays and
OL,20,Fdeveloping the baritone voice that
OL,21,Fwould later define his career.
