OL,6,FHe adopted the stage name "Burton"
OL,7,Ffrom Phillip Burton, his schoolteacher
OL,8,Fand mentor, who became his legal
OL,9,Fguardian and guided him towards a
OL,10,Fcareer in theatre and film.
OL,12,FBurton went on to become one of the
OL,13,Fmost recognisable actors of his
OL,14,Fgeneration, appearing in films such as
OL,15,F'Cleopatra', 'Who's Afraid of Virginia
OL,16,FWoolf?', and 'The Spy Who Came in from
OL,17,Fthe Cold'.
