OL,6,FOver his career, he received seven
OL,7,FAcademy Award nominations and was
OL,8,Frenowned for both his stage and screen
OL,9,Fperformances, as well as his high-
OL,10,Fprofile personal life, including his
OL,11,Fmarriage to Elizabeth Taylor.
OL,13,FAlthough he spent much of his
OL,14,Fprofessional life in the United
OL,15,FStates, those who knew him say he
OL,16,Fnever lost his connection to Wales.
