OL,3,CPlaque to honour 100 years since
OL,4,CHollywood actor Richard Burton's birth
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, his niece
OL,7,FSian Owen recalled his deep affection
OL,8,Ffor his homeland: "He always had
OL,9,Fhiraeth (longing) for the place. He
OL,10,Fused to love coming to Pontrhydyfen
OL,11,Fbecause it was the only time he could
OL,12,Fspeak Welsh, and of course it was his
OL,13,Ffirst language, and he loved it."
OL,15,FShe also highlighted his generosity:
OL,16,F"He set up a family business, and the
OL,17,Fcheques used to arrive for my mother
OL,18,Fand all of his brothers and sisters
OL,19,Fevery August and every Christmas. Mami
OL,20,Fwould be there at the door waiting for
OL,21,Fthe postman to grab the envelope.
