OL,6,F"It was him that bought us the house -
OL,7,Fthey would never have been able to do
OL,8,Fthat without him."
OL,10,FShe added: "He was very, very kind. I
OL,11,Fam so, so proud to be his niece and to
OL,12,Fhave spent so much time in his
OL,13,Fcompany."
OL,15,FToday's centenary event celebrates
OL,16,FBurton's enduring legacy in film and
OL,17,Ftheatre, while also recognising his
OL,18,Flifelong connection to Wales and the
OL,19,Fcommunity that shaped him.
